body:
NOW THIS MOD IS IN BETAS! THIS MOD ISN'T COMPATABLE WITH SURVIVAL YET, BUT SOON IT WILL BE.
 

Now this mod adds 9 new discs! Also, Musics in mod aren't by me. Musics are not copyrighted and they were made by Infraction. If you like musics in mod check him out for more. 

This mod currently adds these discs:
-Good Vibe;
-Heroes;
-Film;
-Exhale;
-Skylight;
-Nature;
-Touch The Hope;
-Politics;
-action.


FEATURES I'M GOING ADD IN FUTURE:

-survival compatibility;
-maybe config to disable not Minecrafty music;
-more musics(Including Rick-Roll).

 
If You Want To See This Mod BETTER The Please Suggest Your Ideas :)

 
Also this mod is made for fabric and i don't have any plans to update it to forge yet.
